		<div class="section-info"><h1>The Guide to Sleeping in Airports</h1><div class="description"><p>Are you stuck in the airport? Do you have a long layover?<br>Would you like to save money on an airport hotel by sleeping in the airport?</p></div><img src="images/home/hm-winter-17.png" alt="The Guide to Sleeping in Airports | image copyright SleepingInAirports.com" width="400" height="321" vspace="10" class="homeIMG"><p>Sure, it may sound a little cheap and degrading at first, but read-on and you'll soon discover a travel community that shares their experiences and advice with fellow airport sleepers.</p><p>Airport sleeping is no longer just for the cheap young backpacker. Nowadays, early morning flights, long layovers, flight cancellations, snow storms and erupting volcanoes are just a few reasons why you'll see travellers from all walks of life stretched out on airport floors around the world.</p><p>Whether you sleep in an airport overnight by choice or you just get stuck in the airport due to a layover or weather delay, let The Guide to Sleeping in Airports help make your travel experience more tolerable.</p><p>Explore our <strong><a href="airport-guides.htm">airport guides</a></strong> and read <strong><a href="https://www.sleepinginairports.net/community/">airport reviews</a></strong> from travellers who survived the dreaded airport sleepover!</p><p class="intro" align="center"><strong>Find an Airport</strong>: <a href="africa/index.htm">Africa</a> &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp; <a href="asia/index.htm">Asia</a> &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp; <a href="casa/index-caribbean-central-am.htm">Caribbean &amp; Central America</a> &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp; <a href="europe/index.htm">Europe</a> &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp; <a href="mideast/index.htm">Middle East</a> &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp; <a href="usa/index.htm">North America</a> &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp; <a href="casa/index-south-america.htm">South America </a>&nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp;<a href="oceania/index.htm"> South Pacific</a></p></div><!-- /.section-info --><div class="list list-home"><ul><li><a href="2016/best-airports.htm"><img src="images/home/best-airports.png" alt="Best Airports of 2017"> <strong>Best Airports of 2017</strong> <span>We asked travellers to rate their overall airport experience. Find out which ones were voted as the Best Airports</span>.</a></li><li><a href="2017/worst-airports.htm"><img src="images/home/worst-airports.png" alt="Worst Airports of 2016" width="160" height="158"> <strong>Worst Airports of 2017</strong> <span>Forget sleeping in these airports. In fact, you'll want to get in and out of these terminals quickly or avoid them altogether.</span></a></li><li><a href="airport-guides.htm"><img src="images/home/airport-guides-3.png" alt="Airport Guides" width="160" height="158"> <strong>Airport Guides</strong> <span>We have over 1200 airport guides giving you the info and user reviews you need to plan your layover or sleepover.</span></a></li><li><a href="tips.htm"><img src="images/home/airport-sleeping-tips.png" alt="Airport Sleeping Tips" width="160" height="158"> <strong>How to sleep in the airport: Airport Sleeping Tips</strong> <span>If you have never slept in an airport before, prepare for your sleepover by reading these tips.</span></a></li><li><a href="airport-lounges/index.htm"><img src="images/home/airport-lounges-home.png" alt="airport lounges" width="158" height="160"> <strong>Airport Lounges</strong> <span>Did you know that you can now buy your way into a first class airport lounge without having to pay for a Business or First Class ticket?</span></a></li><li><a href="hotels/index.htm"><img src="images/home/airport-hotels.png" alt="airport hotels" width="158" height="160"> <strong>Airport Hotels</strong> <span>Not all airport benches are created equal, so check out our airport guides to learn where the nearest hotels or sleep pods are located - just in case.</span></a></li><li><a href="http://blog.sleepinginairports.net/"><img src="images/home/blog.png" alt="Sleeping in Airports Blog" width="160" height="158"> <strong>Blog</strong> <span>Airport and travel related news, articles and announcements.</span></a></li><li><a href="layovers/index.htm"><img src="images/home/sightseeing.png" alt="Airport Layover Sightseeing" width="158" height="160"> <strong>Airport Layover Sightseeing</strong> <span>When you have a long layover, you may want to get out of the airport and do some sightseeing.</span></a></li><li><a href="airports-with-cots.htm"><img src="images/home/airport-cots.png" alt="cots at the airport" width="160" height="158"> <strong>Airport with Cots</strong> <span>Did you know that some airports have a supply of costs for passengers faced with a flight delay due to a major weather disruption?</span></a></li><li><a href="http://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/3917521/2018-Survey"><img src="images/home/survey.png" alt="2017 Airport Survey" width="160" height="158"> <strong>Take our 2018 Airport Survey</strong> <span>Help us determine the Best & Worst Airports by participating in our 2018 Airport Survey!</span></a></li></ul><div class="clear"></div></div><!-- /.list --><div class="<em>popular-airports</em>"><h3>Our Most Popular Airport Guides</h3><p><a href="mideast/dubai.htm">Dubai</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/seoul.htm">Seoul Incheon</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/kualalumpur.htm">Kuala Lumpur</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/singapore.htm">Singapore Changi</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/bangkok.htm">Bangkok</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/hongkong.htm">Hong Kong</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="usa/new-york-jfk-airport.htm">New York City JFK</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="mideast/doha.htm">Doha Hamad</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="usa/losangeles.htm">Los Angeles</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/taipei.htm">Taipei Taoyuan</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="europe/londonheathrow.htm">London Heathrow</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/manila.htm">Manila NAIA</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/delhi.htm">New Delhi</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="europe/paris.htm">Paris Charles de Gaulle</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="europe/amsterdam.htm">Amsterdam Schiphol</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="europe/frankfurt.htm">Frankfurt am Main</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/beijing.htm">Beijing</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/shanghai.htm">Shanghai Pudong</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/bombay.htm">Mumbai</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="europe/istanbul.htm">Istanbul Ataturk</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="usa/chicago_ohare.htm">Chicago O'Hare</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="usa/sanfrancisco.htm">San Francisco</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/guangzhou.htm">Guangzhou</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/tokyo_haneda.htm">Tokyo Haneda</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/ho-chi-minh-city-airport.htm">Ho Chi Minh City</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="northamerica/toronto-airport.htm">Toronto Pearson</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="usa/atlanta.htm">Atlanta</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/chennai.htm">Chennai</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="asia/tokyo_narita.htm">Tokyo Narita</a> &nbsp; &#8226; &nbsp; <a href="europe/barcelonaprat.htm">Barcelona El Prat</a></p><div class="clear"></div></div><!-- /.popular airports --><div class="about-logos"><p align="center"><strong>mentioned in:</strong><br><a href="inthenews.htm"><img src="images/logos/logo-frommers.jpg" alt="Frommers.com" width="81" height="54" border="0" class="logo-from"></a><a href="inthenews.htm"><img src="images/logos/logo-time.jpg" width="110" height="54" border="0" class="logo-time"></a><a href="inthenews.htm"><img src="images/logos/logo-reuters.jpg" width="189" height="54" alt="reuters" class="logo-reut"></a><a href="inthenews.htm"><img src="images/logos/logo-nyt.jpg" width="241" height="54" border="0" class="logo-nyt"></a><a href="inthenews.htm"><img src="images/logos/logo-usa-today.jpg" width="81" height="54" alt="usa today" class="logo-us